skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: your health matters greatly
des: When this skill is activated, you listen to interesting and educative health facts and tips that will help you live a better and healthier life everyday. The information presented in this skill is for informational and educational purposes only, and not intended to diagnose or treat any medical condition. Please follow up with your health care provider as necessary.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
